{"tid":2195337,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"獲威尼斯影展金獅終身成就獎　許鞍華：想將榮譽給香港","createTime":"2020-09-09T06:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T07:25:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d0866287a55e3c3738543289455afd8552360ef0","tid":2195337,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:13:13.000Z","msg":"香港著名導演許鞍華獲頒威尼斯電影節金獅終身成就獎，成為威尼斯電影節史上，首位獲得這項榮譽的女導演。<br />\n<br />\n由許鞍華執導，改編自張愛玲小說的電影《第一爐香》，入圍今年威尼斯電影節非競賽部分。73歲的許鞍華在頒獎儀式上說，在艱難的當下，這個獎給她及香港人帶來鼓勵，她想將這項榮譽帶給香港，因為香港是她長大，並度過人生的地方，給她教育、生活經歷及機會去實現自我價值，她會幫助年輕的電影人，令他們將來都能夠獲得終身成就獎。<br />\n<br />\n被問到政見問題，許鞍華說，她最好不發表太多評論，因為這部電影由中國公司出資，有關公司亦容許拍攝這部在道德上極複雜的電影，只是刪減了極少就通過審查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548664-20200909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548664-20200909.htm&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg3dT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=62fa37b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548664-20200909.htm&h=901dd400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548664-20200909.htm</a>"},{"pid":"97fd0974b494eb1f6d351293c4d6f7c908ae3279","tid":2195337,"uid":228995,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:48:01.000Z","msg":"有睇《明月幾時有》<br />\n就會明白Ann姐"},{"pid":"9176f3418a112a2bfb43f2efe7e50a9fe06d1e83","tid":2195337,"uid":53498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"97fd0974b494eb1f6d351293c4d6f7c908ae3279","tid":2195337,"uid":228995,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:48:01.000Z","msg":"有睇《明月幾時有》<br />\n就會明白Ann姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"仲有投奔怒海"},{"pid":"e847d59cc2ffae8a5b1642dcb4cff77059602918","tid":2195337,"uid":26764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97fd0974b494eb1f6d351293c4d6f7c908ae3279","tid":2195337,"uid":228995,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy